{"id":281786,"type":6,"name":"Stargirl","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/77/54/281786_MDNcf.jpg","summary":"　　DC首席创意官Geoff Johns离任后，他改为联合Greg Berlanti及Sarah Schechter为网上频道DC Universe开发DC英雄剧《逐星女 Stargirl》，这个角色在漫画中亦是由Geoff Johns所创作。在首季13集的剧集版中，高中生Courtney Whitmore（Brec Bassinger饰）将成为逐星女，加入美国正义协会/Justice Society of America对抗起各种反派。 \r\n　　在漫画中Courtney Whitmore找到继父藏着的天空侠（前闪星小子）装备，于是她穿上装备并成为了闪星小子二代（原因是报复继父娶了她的母亲）。不过在后来得知继父其实也是个英雄，以及得到星杖当武器后，她改称为逐星女/ Stargirl。该角色曾经在《超人前传 Smallville》及《明日传奇 DC's Legends of Tomorrow》登场，分别由Britt Irvin及Sarah Grey饰演。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>逐星女</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期日</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/24742\">DC Comics</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>星女</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2020-05-18</li><li><span>结束: </span>2020-08-10</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作 / 科幻</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>53分钟</li><li><span>电视网: </span>DC Universe</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>美国</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt8722888</li><li><span>编剧: </span>乔夫·琼斯</li><li><span>主演: </span>布瑞克·巴辛格 / 维特·蒙雷尔 / 克里斯托弗·杰姆斯·贝克 / 乔尔·麦克哈尔 / 布瑞恩·斯塔夫 / 卢克·威尔逊 / 小卢·弗里基诺 / 乔伊·奥斯曼斯基 / 尼尔·霍普金斯 / 尼尔森·李 / 卡梅伦·格尔曼 / 艾米·斯马特 / 尼尔·杰克逊</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"doing":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"DC","count":2},{"name":"美剧","count":2}],"eps":[{"id":880871,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/880871","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Pilot","name_cn":"","duration":"50m","airdate":"2020-05-18","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":880872,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/880872","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"S.T.R.I.P.E.","name_cn":"","duration":"50m","airdate":"2020-05-25","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":880873,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/880873","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"Icicle","name_cn":"","duration":"50m","airdate":"2020-06-01","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":880874,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/880874","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"Wildcat","name_cn":"","duration":"50m","airdate":"2020-06-08","c